        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>National Commission on Scleroderma and Fibrotic Diseases Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill temporarily establishes a National Commission on Fibrotic Diseases within the National Institutes of Health that must recommend improvements regarding fibrosis and fibrotic disease research.</p>]]></text>
